// --- Commit Message Rules ---
All commits must follow Conventional Commits format, e.g.:
  feat(auth): add login via magic link
  fix(ui): prevent flicker on re-render
  chore(deps): bump react from 18.2 to 19.0

If AI generates a commit message, enforce:
  - lowercase type (e.g. feat, fix, chore)
  - scope in parentheses if relevant
  - colon + space
  - imperative tone (e.g. "add", not "adds")

